  dxSkinOffice2007Black, dxSkinOffice2007Blue, dxSkinOffice2007Green, dxSkinOffice2007Pink, dxSkinOffice2007Silver,
  dxSkinOffice2010Black, dxSkinOffice2010Blue, dxSkinOffice2010Silver, dxSkinOffice2013DarkGray,
